 our Top Ten Reviews, is that it does not carry brandable clothing and is a bit sparse in some of its other categories. But, if your choice for business giveaways is a personalized pen, you owe it to your company to check out the exceptional selection at National Pen.","<strong>Imprinted.com</strong><br/>While it offers many of the items in the categories we rank in our promotional product store review, Imprinted.com is also a company that did not make our review, because you can t buy an embroidered shirt on their site. However, the company offers a huge selection of merchandise that comes with free shipping. They also have fabulous deals on a wide selection of hats. So, if free shipping would help or you re in the market for hats, this site is well worth a look.","<strong>DiscountMugs</strong><br/>One of the companies that did make our review is DiscountMugs. This company started out as one of the largest U.S. drinkware suppliers. Over the past few years, it s grown to include all of the categories required for our review. However, glass is still their forte, and if that s what you re looking for, this company is a great place to start. The company s glassware includes beer mugs, wine glasses, champagne flutes, shot glasses, martini glasses, brandy snifters, candy jars and even votive candle holders.","While purchasers of promotional items may find the sites in our review offer a single point of contact, if you have a specific product in mind, you may find greater variety and savings at an online store that is not quite a one-stop shop."]},"id":"5c57d42a-4cd7-40d6-9157-c9d390755d23","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_9233","url":"/category-specific-promotional-products","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"lynda-angelastro","url":"/author/lynda-angelastro","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Lynda Angelastro","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"iJqwET8ThNWCtNBejE3QeP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","G